CommonUtilsLib provides common utility functions for Qt and Xlsx operations.

To use in your CMake project:

    find_package(CommonUtilsLib CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(your-target PRIVATE CommonUtilsLib::CommonUtilsLib)

Example usage:

    #include <CommonUtils/common_utils.h>

    common_utils utils;
    std::string formatted = utils.stringFormat("  hello world  ");
